mx-toolkit:
  v 0.0.4 - 02/19/2014
  --------------------
  * Implement 'flash erase' feature
  * Provide useful error messages for several error cases in the
    mx-toolkit driver, including invalid addresses, sizes, etc.
  * Warn if missing the memory initialization file
  * Provide stubbed out RAM kernel and memory init file configurations
    in the default bspinfo.conf.
  * Allow for terminal widths of at least 80 characters
  * Use %APPDATA%\pyatk on Windows for configuration files instead of the user's
    %HOME%\.pyatk
